HEADWORD: Peppercorn
<hw>Pep"per*corn`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
dried berry of the black pepper (<spn>Piper nigrum</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Anything insignificant; a particle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pepper dulse</ent>⟦br⟧
